{
  "chapter": 25,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十五回　神驴铁胆。剑客行故事继续。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们就猜这来人的身份。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "骑驴",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神驴铁胆",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "几百招也不在乎！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰！砰！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神驴铁胆",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们为什么要打呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不知道他们为什么打。我来到这里找你没找到，却碰到他们，说是已经打了三天三夜，掌拳兵器，武功内力，什么都比过了，还是分不出高下，才请我当裁判，叫我出主意使他们分出胜败来，可是，我想尽方法，他们仍是不输不赢，你来的时候，我正要他们比赛",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我倒问你，你在兴隆酒店，被",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "噢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死人居",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们两个娃儿，尽管唠叨没完！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗬……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喳！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰！砰！……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗡！嗡！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘴中说着话，右手单拐漫不经心地向上一撩，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叮！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叮！叮！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哈！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如何",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不能再加多了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金音，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "雷音佛掌！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好大的掌力！一个人能修炼到这种程度，的确使人不可思议……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你父亲！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你明知道，还问什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，你为什么不随父姓慕容，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是当真善忘，还是故意装糊涂？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上的人，通常都是随父姓，很少跟母姓。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不相信我，以为我会说谎吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展哥哥，去不得！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "的一声，不但未能前进，反而把展白倒震出数步，气翻血涌，双耳雷鸣，不由暗暗咋舌道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "展哥哥，你伤到了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不妨事……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老怪物，你还活着吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放心！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着也从怀中掏出一包药粉吞下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "彼此！彼此！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是老夫！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神猴",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "神猴",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听到提起他的弟子，神猴脸上立刻变为恨毒，咬牙说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着一指他断去的双腿道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这番话听得展白和婉儿，也是义愤填膺，常言道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是两个孽徒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说罢兀自叹息不已。神驴铁胆董千里，也是捶胸顿足，恼悔不已，道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 25,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    }
  ],
